extends baseEmail 

block content                              
    p Hi #{firstName},
    p Forgot your password? Submit a PATCH request with your new password and passwordConfirmed to: 
    p #{url} 
    p (Website for this action coming soon, maybe!)
    table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
        tbody
            tr
                td(align='left')
                    table(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
                        tbody
                            tr
                                td
                                    a(href=`${url}`, target='_blank') Reset your password
    p This token is only valid for 10 minutes, so if you don't make it in time, you'll need to request a new password reset!
    p If you didn't forget your password, please ignore this email.